keys to move the helicopter:
----------------------------
'd' - down nose of the helicopter.
'u' - up nose of the helicopter.
'+' - zoom in.
'-' - zoom out.
'/' - tilt left.
'*' - tilt right.
'8' - up.                  -+
'2' - down.                 | num lock arrow keyes.
'4' - left.                 |
'6' - right.               -+

'q' - quit.

